57 leaders will be empowered to continue building a legacy of
58 service and excellence; now therefore,
59 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE
60 LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, That Mr. Robert James Richardson
61 will be highly honored on an unforgettable afternoon filled
62 with inspiration, celebration, and community, and we
63 endeavor to continue uplifting and investing in those who
64 make a difference, both today and tomorrow.
